posting_body: ['The Village at Ten Trails', '22870 SE FIR STREET, Black Diamond, WA, 98010', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 62', 'Connections.', 'Adventures.', 'Home.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 670 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Village at Ten Trails is a community within a community.', 'Live amid the stunning natural beauty of the Pacific Northwest, with wooded trails, parks, a town center with retail village, a school and residences all combining to create an interactive atmosphere.', 'We like to call it your new hometown.', 'Apartment homes ranging from one to three bedrooms are now pre-leasing, offering high-end finishes, thoughtful touches and comfortable spaces to make your own.', 'Features', '- In-home washer and dryer', '- Electric fireplaces (in select homes)', '- Quartz countertops', '- Private balconies on floors 2 and above', '- Stainless steel appliances', '- Oversized windows', '- 9-foot ceilings (18 feet on top floor)', 'Community Amenities', '- Centrally located between Maple Valley, Covington, Kent and Enumclaw', '- Picnic areas', '- Playgrounds', '- Community events', '- Hiking trails nearby', '- Future retail', '- Wave Broadband Gigabit Internet Access', 'Office Hours', 'Mon, Wed, Fri - 9am-6pm', 'Tues and Thurs - 10am-6pm', 'Sat and Sun - 10am-5pm', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'qufnZ56r']
